# Cloudflare Pages response headers.
# Deployed from apps/studio/build/_headers (the deploy workflow copies this
# file into the export output directory before wrangler upload).
#
# CSP frame-ancestors restricts who can iframe Studio. Tighten once the
# architecture-viewer is bound to a stable subdomain (e.g. architecture.archally.dev)
# and remove *.pages.dev from the allowlist.

/*
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors https://*.archally.dev https://*.pages.dev
  Referrer-Policy: same-origin
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
